sops.sop:
Workflow:
1. User -> Transportation Planner;
2. Transportation Planner -> Accommodation Planner 
   Transportation Planner -> Restaurant Planner 
   Transportation -> Attractions Planner (in parallel);
3. Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, Attractions Planner -> Plan Checker;
4. Plan Checker -> Final Plan Summarizer;
5. Final Plan Summarizer -> End.

Description:
First, the Transportation Planner determines inter-city transportation and daily locations. This framework guides the Accommodation Planner (private room bookings), Restaurant Planner (meals for two), and Attractions Planner (free Orlando activities) working in parallel. The Plan Checker verifies budget adherence ($2000 total) and logistical consistency. Finally, the Summarizer creates a detailed itinerary including flight numbers, exact accommodation names, restaurant selections, and attraction details following the specified format.
